    <item>
      <title>荷兰央行行长表示需要数字欧元来实现自治</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/dutch-central-banker-says-digital-euro-is-needed-for-autonomy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[荷兰央行行长克拉斯·诺特周五表示，欧洲需要数字欧元“以跟上社会的步伐，追求战略自主权，并在数字世界中保持获得公共资金的机会”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/dutch-central-banker-says-digital-euro-is-needed-for-autonomy</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 16:28:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗要求美国靠边站，准备对以色列做出回应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/iran-tells-us-to-step-aside-as-it-readies-response-to-israel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗表示，在该国准备对以色列驻叙利亚领事馆涉嫌袭击事件做出回应之际，它要求美国“靠边站”，而其在中东的主要代理人真主党则警告这个犹太国家，它已做好战争准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/iran-tells-us-to-step-aside-as-it-readies-response-to-israel</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 16:02:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰能源公司计划重建一半受损设施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/ukraine-energy-firm-plans-to-rebuild-half-of-damaged-facilities</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰最大的私营能源公司 DTEK BV 寻求最早在 6 月恢复近一半的受损设施，这些设施在最近的俄罗斯袭击中成为目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/ukraine-energy-firm-plans-to-rebuild-half-of-damaged-facilities</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 15:50:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>内塔尼亚胡进入拉法的计划在以色列面临越来越多的反对</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/israel-s-plan-to-attack-rafah-faces-growing-opposition-after-us-pressure</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国的压力下，一些以色列重要人物敦促政府放弃入侵加沙南部城市拉法的计划，并表示停火和释放人质应该是首要任务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/israel-s-plan-to-attack-rafah-faces-growing-opposition-after-us-pressure</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 15:49:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着外交关系持续解冻，中美恢复军事会议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/us-china-resume-military-meetings-as-diplomatic-thaw-continues</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国和中国恢复了防务对话，旨在防止意外冲突，这是恢复指挥系统上下接触的更广泛努力的一部分，这些接触近年来因台湾和南海领土争端的紧张局势加剧而中断。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/us-china-resume-military-meetings-as-diplomatic-thaw-continues</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 15:33:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普 SPAC 证词定于同日刑事审判开始</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/trump-deposed-in-spac-lawsuit-the-day-of-start-of-criminal-trial</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 定于 4 月 15 日在与其社交媒体初创公司有关的民事诉讼中接受质询，同日这位前总统的首次刑事审判也将开始。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/trump-deposed-in-spac-lawsuit-the-day-of-start-of-criminal-trial</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 14:31:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>冰岛总理辞职竞选总统</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/iceland-s-prime-minister-steps-down-to-run-for-president</link>
      <description><![CDATA[冰岛总理卡特琳·雅各布斯多蒂尔将在下次大选前一年辞职，竞选总统，此举可能会让她的环保势力失去这个北大西洋国家的总理职位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/iceland-s-prime-minister-steps-down-to-run-for-president</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 13:26:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国即将公布巴尔的摩大桥调查的初步结果</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/us-set-to-release-preliminary-results-of-baltimore-bridge-probe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联邦官员准备公布巴尔的摩大桥倒塌事件的初步调查结果，该事件造成六人死亡，并导致巴尔的摩港口上周关闭。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/us-set-to-release-preliminary-results-of-baltimore-bridge-probe</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 21:07:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯为何入侵乌克兰？了解战争的根源</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-09/why-did-russia-invade-ukraine-understanding-the-roots-of-the-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯总统普京多次明确表示，他认为乌克兰的地位处于俄罗斯的控制之下。从 18 世纪叶卡捷琳娜大帝统治下的俄罗斯帝国时代到苏联各国的共同历史，它的立场都是如此。近年来，历届乌克兰政府都与欧盟和北约建立了更密切的关系，然后又向俄罗斯靠拢，然后又再次疏远。普京意在通过战争来决定乌克兰的走向]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-09/why-did-russia-invade-ukraine-understanding-the-roots-of-the-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 15:28:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
